<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{{ ansible_hostname }} - Servidor Configurado con Ansible</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            min-height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(31, 38, 135, 0.37);
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 2.5em;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
        }
        .info-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .info-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            backdrop-filter: blur(5px);
        }
        .info-card h3 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: #ffeb3b;
        }
        .status-indicator {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 12px;
            height: 12px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #4caf50;
            margin-right: 8px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }
        @keyframes pulse {
            0% { opacity: 1; }
            50% { opacity: 0.5; }
            100% { opacity: 1; }
        }
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        .links {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .links a {
            color: #ffeb3b;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 0 15px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: 2px solid #ffeb3b;
            border-radius: 25px;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .links a:hover {
            background-color: #ffeb3b;
            color: #333;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üöÄ Servidor Web Configurado</h1>
            <p><span class="status-indicator"></span>Terraform + Ansible en acci√≥n</p>
        </div>

        <div class="info-grid">
            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üñ•Ô∏è Informaci√≥n del Servidor</h3>
                <p><strong>Hostname:</strong> {{ ansible_hostname }}</p>
                <p><strong>IP Address:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
                <p><strong>Sistema Operativo:</strong> {{ ansible_distribution }} {{ ansible_distribution_version }}</p>
                <p><strong>Arquitectura:</strong> {{ ansible_architecture }}</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üíæ Recursos del Sistema</h3>
                <p><strong>Memoria Total:</strong> {{ (ansible_memtotal_mb/1024) | round(2) }} GB</p>
                <p><strong>CPUs:</strong> {{ ansible_processor_count }} cores</p>
                <p><strong>Modelo CPU:</strong> {{ ansible_processor[2] | default('N/A') }}</p>
                <p><strong>Uptime:</strong> {{ ansible_uptime_seconds | int // 3600 }}h {{ (ansible_uptime_seconds | int % 3600) // 60 }}m</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>üåê Configuraci√≥n de Red</h3>
                <p><strong>IP P√∫blica:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.address }}</p>
                <p><strong>Gateway:</strong> {{ ansible_default_ipv4.gateway | default('N/A') }}</p>
                <p><strong>DNS:</strong> {{ ansible_dns.nameservers | join(', ') | default('N/A') }}</p>
                <p><strong>Interfaces:</strong> {{ ansible_interfaces | length }} detectadas</p>
            </div>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>‚öôÔ∏è Estado de Servicios</h3>
                <p><strong>Apache HTTP:</strong> <span style="color: #4caf50;">‚úÖ Activo</span></p>
                <p><strong>SSH:</strong> <span style="color: #4caf50;">‚úÖ Activo</span></p>
                <p><strong>Firewall:</strong> <span style="color: #4caf50;">‚úÖ Configurado</span></p>
                <p><strong>√öltima actualizaci√≥n:</strong> {{ ansible_date_time.date }}</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="links">
            <a href="/info.html">üìä Info Detallada</a>
            <a href="/backup/">üìÅ Backups</a>
            <a href="https://github.com/ansible/ansible" target="_blank">üìö Ansible Docs</a>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>üîß Configurado autom√°ticamente con <strong>Ansible</strong> | 
               ‚òÅÔ∏è Provisionado con <strong>Terraform</strong> | 
               üìÖ {{ ansible_date_time.date }} {{ ansible_date_time.time }}</p>
            <p>üè∑Ô∏è Proyecto: {{ project | default('terraform-ansible-lab') }} | 
               üåç Entorno: {{ environment | default('production') }}</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
